HEADWORD: Ptosis
<hw>Pto"sis</hw> <pr>(t⟦omac⟧"s⟦icr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>ptw^sis</grk> a falling.]</ety>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Drooping of the upper eyelid, produced by
paralysis of its levator muscle.</def>⟦br⟧
